                            W water
                            G level ground
                            M mountains
                            A atmosphere
                            F force of the earth's
                            attraction
                        </figDesc>
                    </figure>
                <pb/> 
                    <p>
                        A projectile shot steeply upwards rises through 
                        the air with diminishing intensity, turns, and falls 
                        with increasing intensity back to the earth.
                    </p>
